**In the center of the image, draw a sword-wielding warrior standing in a heroic pose, with one foot forward and one foot back. The warrior wears a dark outfit with a hood that partially obscures their face, giving them a shadowy and mysterious appearance. The sword the warrior holds appears to be glowing with an otherworldly energy. Behind the warrior, draw a swirling vortex of energy, which represents the multiverse. In the vortex, draw various different versions of the warrior, each holding a different weapon and wearing a different outfit.
